            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Alamundus">Alamundus</name></persName> filius
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Maria">Marie</name></persName> riceve in
                        livello da <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/203">Unichisus</persName>
                        gratia dei <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/86">sede
                            sancte <placeName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#places/86"
                                >Populoniensis</placeName>
                            <rs key="#Mother_churches">ecclesie</rs></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> (…) <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casa et sorte</rs> (…) in loco <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Petiae" ref="#places/276"
                            >Oliveto</placeName> qui pertine de <rs key="#Baptismal_churches"
                            >plebe</rs> vestra baptismalis beati <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/192">Sancti Quirici</orgName> sito <placeName
                            key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#places/276">Oliveto</placeName> quod est
                        infra <rs key="#Comitatus">comitato</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/87">Populoniense</geogName>, (…)
                        qui iam recta fuit per <persName><name ref="Berno">Berno</name></persName>
                        et modo recta est autem per <persName><name ref="Amalbertus"
                                >Amalperto</name></persName>; riceve inoltre una <rs key="#Petiae"
                            >petia</rs> de terra in eodem loco Oliveto et est pertinentes de de
                        plebe baptismalis beati Sancti Quirici, quem <persName key="#Other_clerics"
                                ><name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfredus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> ad manum suam detinere visus fuit,
                        una cum cesis et omnibus arboribus e tutte le loro dipendenze. Si impegna a
                        versare al vescovo e ai suoi successori ad ecclesia et Sancti Quirici sita
                        loco Oliveto pensionem argentum denarios duodecim boni expendibilis qualis
                        per tempore occurrunt per nos aut per missus noster vobis vel ad <rs
                            key="#Actionarii/actores">actor</rs> vester de ipsa ecclesia Sancti
                        Quirici de Oliveto aut in ipsa ecclesia mittantur tantum. Se non rispetterà
                        i suddetti impegni, promette con i suoi eredi e proeredi di versare al
                        vescovo e ai suoi successori la pena di 100 soldi d’argento. Chiede ad
                        Andrea notaio [e scabino] la stesura di due cartule. Actum <placeName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#places/91">Kornino</placeName> ad <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/127">Sancti
                        Iusti</orgName>. Sottoscrivono: Alamundus; <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Isalbertus">Isalbertus</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Stefanus">Stefano</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Roppaldus">Roppaldi</name></persName> filius
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Rotardus">Rotardi</name></persName>;
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Auripertus"
                            >Auriperti</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Stefanus"
                                >Stefani</name></persName>; Scrive: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Scabini" ref="#people/260">Andreas</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs></ab>
                        </div>
